 286:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_gpio.c **** /**
 287:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_gpio.c ****   * @brief  De-initialize the GPIOx peripheral registers to their default reset values.
 288:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_gpio.c ****   * @param  GPIOx where x can be (A..G) to select the GPIO peripheral for STM32G4xx family
 289:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_gpio.c ****   * @param  GPIO_Pin specifies the port bit to be written.
 290:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *         This parameter can be any combination of GPIO_PIN_x where x can be (0..15).
